<plot>Farmer Al Falfa is a patrolman rollerskating through the park. His day's misadventures including boxing a kangaroo, quarreling with a nanny, chasing after juvenile baby-nappers, sparring with a monkey, playing tug of war with an ostrich and suffering the pranks of a pair of mischievous bear cubs. Finally, the monkey calls the police and then steals Al Falfa's clothes. The poor old man is soon set upon by his fellow cops, who don't realize that he's a cop, too: all they see is an old man indecently wearing nothing but his underwear.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?130590</url></doc>
